snippet.title: Final Fantasy 1 Origins HD Normal Mode Chapter 1 Part 1 The Adventure Begins
snippet.description:
Final Fantasy 1

Chapter 1 part 1
1. Pick up your characters & Name them.
2. Setup your Config.
3. Buy weapons, Armour & Spells you might need 
4. Talk to the King
5. Leveling up (200 Battles outside Cornelia)(Do your battles at the by the bridge area & Outside the Temple of Chaos)
Buy some Antidote & Sleeping Bags if you want to do battles inside the Temple of Chaos
Its worth it
